{"tid":666883,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔係咪一定要絕育？","createTime":"2018-05-16T09:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T10:14:39.000Z","uid":163622,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa7e7e918ba3765e3ae004b6d0d90a01a99cd27","tid":666883,"uid":163622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"第一次養貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英短 9個半月<br />\n試過發情，例如奶J，漏尿<br />\n但唔會帶好多麻煩比我，例如亂屙尿果d都冇，好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有做過資料搜集 一般來說絕育好似係對貓女的好處係大d，但對貓仔來說冇咩特別好處<br />\n話就話貓仔絕育後會乖d唔會成日叫，週圍屙<br />\n但我隻貓真係好乖 其實係咪唔絕都得？<br />\n身邊d朋友不停問我幾時帶去絕又講到唔帶去絕就係對貓唔好咁<br />\n但唔想佢無啦啦挨一刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c2e9a718af55c63d4d11cbf28a528328c036cc","tid":666883,"uid":172733,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"奶j <br />\n<br />\n但又貓女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4593cb2759c0ab7b9b4e2e2b7d192ba356c9d278","tid":666883,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5823e7555e6ab2d1cc9c371e974e5403baac6519","tid":666883,"uid":163622,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b4c2e9a718af55c63d4d11cbf28a528328c036cc","tid":666883,"uid":172733,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"奶j <br />\n<br />\n但又貓女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"清 標題寫咗係貓仔"},{"pid":"3a42b29acf7d95c959b98c3a3999902591c538b2","tid":666883,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e8fa300a0a5213def9c4